        <div class="contact-grid">
            <div class="contact-info-card">
                <h3>Direct Inquiries</h3>
                <p><strong>Business Name:</strong> Leeway Rides</p>
                <p><strong>Affiliated Network:</strong> LTS Connect Network</p>
                <p><strong>Phone / Text:</strong> <a href="sms:+19803923216" style="color: var(--accent-gold);">980-392-3216</a></p>
                <p><strong>Business Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:Leewayridesnow@gmail.com" style="color: var(--accent-gold);">Leewayridesnow@gmail.com</a>[cite: 1]</p>
                <p><strong>Service Location:</strong> Based in Shelby, NC (Serving Cleveland County, Gastonia, Charlotte, Rock Hill, Spartanburg, and surrounding regional areas).</p>
                <p><strong>Operating Hours:</strong> Transportation available 24 hours by advance reservation.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="contact-info-card">
                <h3>Emergency Notice</h3>
                <p style="color: #ffcf68;"><strong>Important:</strong> Leeway Rides provides non-emergency private transportation and is not an ambulance service or emergency medical provider.</p>
                <p>If you or a passenger are experiencing a sudden medical emergency, please dial 911 immediately.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Partnership Section Integrated into Contact Page -->
        <div class="lead-form-box">
            <h3>Business & Referral Partnerships</h3>
            <p style="color: #ddd; margin-bottom: 15px;">Leeway Rides collaborates with organizations, facilities, and corporations that require dependable, professional transportation solutions for clients, members, patients, residents, or employees.</p>
            <ul class="styled-list">
                <li>Hospitals, medical offices, oncology & dialysis centers</li>
                <li>Rehabilitation facilities & assisted-living communities</li>
                <li>Adult day programs, home-care agencies & group homes</li>
                <li>Case-management organizations & behavioral-health providers</li>
                <li>Churches, nonprofits, employers & corporate travel coordinators</li>
            </ul>
            <p style="color: var(--light-gold); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 20px;">Need dependable transportation for your clients, patients, residents, or employees? Complete the inquiry form below:</p>

            <form action="mailto:Leewayridesnow@gmail.com" method="post" enctype="text/plain" class="form-grid">
                <input type="hidden" name="Source" value="Partnership Page Inquiry on Contact Page">
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label>Organization Name *</label>
                    <input type="text" name="OrgName" required placeholder="Organization Name">
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label>Contact Person *</label>
                    <input type="text" name="ContactPerson" required placeholder="Full Name">
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label>Job Title</label>
                    <input type="text" name="JobTitle" placeholder="Title / Role">
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label>Phone Number *</label>
                    <input type="tel" name="Phone" required placeholder="980-392-3216">
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label>Email Address *</label>
                    <input type="email" name="Email" required placeholder="example@organization.com">
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label>Type of Organization</label>
                    <input type="text" name="OrgType" placeholder="Medical, Senior Living, Corporate...">
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label>Estimated Trip Frequency</label>
                    <input type="text" name="Frequency" placeholder="Daily, Weekly, As needed...">
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label>Service Area / Location</label>
                    <input type="text" name="ServiceArea" placeholder="Shelby, Charlotte, Gastonia...">
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label>Number of Passengers Typically Transported</label>
                    <input type="text" name="PassengerVolume" placeholder="Approximate volume">
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label>Desired Start Date</label>
                    <input type="text" name="StartDate" placeholder="Timeline">
                </div>
                <div class="form-group full-width">
                    <label>Is Invoicing / Corporate Billing Needed?</label>
                    <select name="InvoicingNeeded">
                        <option value="Yes">Yes, require monthly or periodic invoicing</option>
                        <option value="No">No / Flexible</option>
                    </select>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group full-width">
                    <label>Additional Partnership Details</label>
                    <textarea name="Notes" rows="3" placeholder="Share specific requirements or scope..."></textarea>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group full-width">
                    <button type="submit" class="btn-gold" style="width: 100%; padding: 14px;">Submit Partnership Inquiry</button>
                </div>
            </form>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-section">
            <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
            
            <div class="faq-item">
                <h4>How do I request transportation?</h4>
                <p>Complete our online booking calendar or contact Leeway Rides by phone or text. Please provide your pickup address, destination, date, time, passenger count, and trip type.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-item">
                <h4>How far in advance should I schedule?</h4>
                <p>Advance scheduling is strongly recommended. Same-day requests may be considered based on driver availability, but transportation is not guaranteed until confirmed.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-item">
                <h4>Is booking through the calendar a confirmed ride?</h4>
                <p>Online bookings and requests are subject to confirmation and availability by our team.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-item">
                <h4>Do you provide one-way and round-trip transportation?</h4>
                <p>Yes. Customers may request one-way, round-trip, recurring, local, or out-of-town transportation.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-item">
                <h4>Do you provide medical transportation?</h4>
                <p>We provide scheduled, non-emergency transportation for ambulatory passengers traveling to medical appointments and healthcare facilities. We are not an ambulance or emergency medical service.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-item">
                <h4>Do you provide transportation for seniors?</h4>
                <p>Yes. We serve seniors who need dependable transportation to appointments, errands, family visits, senior programs, and other approved destinations.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-item">
                <h4>Can a family member or caregiver arrange transportation?</h4>
                <p>Yes. A family member, caregiver, case manager, facility, or authorized representative may submit a request on behalf of the passenger.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-item">
                <h4>Can I schedule recurring rides?</h4>
                <p>Yes. Recurring transportation may be arranged for work, dialysis, therapy, medical appointments, senior programs, or other ongoing needs, subject to availability.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-item">
                <h4>Do you provide airport transportation?</h4>
                <p>Yes. Airport trips should be scheduled in advance. Customers should provide their airline, flight number, departure or arrival time, passenger count, and luggage details.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-item">
                <h4>Do you provide out-of-town transportation?</h4>
                <p>Yes, depending on availability. Long-distance and out-of-state trips require advance scheduling and a customized quote.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-item">
                <h4>How is pricing determined?</h4>
                <p>Pricing depends on mileage, pickup and drop-off locations, trip timing, number of stops, passenger needs, waiting requirements, and whether the trip is one way or round trip.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-item">
                <h4>What happens if I need to cancel or reschedule?</h4>
                <p>Customers should contact Leeway Rides as soon as possible. Cancellation or no-show charges may apply depending on timing and circumstances.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-item">
                <h4>Do you accept emergency transportation requests?</h4>
                <p>No. Leeway Rides does not provide emergency medical transportation. Call 911 for emergencies.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
